 ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Alice Bucton was born in 1253, in Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom, her father, William Bucton, was 28 and her mother, Mrs. William Bucton, was 23. She married John Bourdon II in 1274, in Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1253–":"1253–Surnud","1253–Female":"1253–Surnud","1250–Male":"1250–Surnud","1275–Male":"1275–Surnud","1225–Male":"1225–Surnud","1230–Female":"1230–Surnud","1225":"1225","1253":"1253","1275":"1275","1274":"1274","1230":"1230","1250":"1250","Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England","Sedgebrook, , Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1253–":"1253–Kuollut","1253–Female":"1253–Kuollut","1250–Male":"1250–Kuollut","1275–Male":"1275–Kuollut","1225–Male":"1225–Kuollut","1230–Female":"1230–Kuollut","1225":"1225","1253":"1253","1275":"1275","1274":"1274","1230":"1230","1250":"1250","Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England","Sedgebrook, , Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1253–":"1253–Décédée","1253–Female":"1253–Décédée","1250–Male":"1250–Décédé","1275–Male":"1275–Décédé","1225–Male":"1225–Décédé","1230–Female":"1230–Décédée","1225":"1225","1253":"1253","1275":"1275","1274":"1274","1230":"1230","1250":"1250","Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, Angleterre","Sedgebrook, , Lincolnshire, England":"Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Alice Bucton est née en 1253, à Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, William Bucton, avait 28 ans et sa mère, Mrs. William Bucton, avait 23 ans. Elle a épousé John Bourdon II en 1274, à Sedgebrook, Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1253–":"1253–Verstorben","1253–Female":"1253–Verstorben","1250–Male":"1250–Verstorben","1275–Male":"